Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.98,0:17:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只我 而是所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒死我們 餓死我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只好躲躲藏藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.70,0:17:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獵魔師毫無慈悲心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我派人監視他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.18,0:17:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再也不用害怕葛瑞戈裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.66,0:17:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我美麗的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開 讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.14,0:19:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿濕鞋是打不贏惡靈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.38,0:19:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修好你的鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去買生活補給品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.26,0:19:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,<font color="#ffcc00"><I>酒館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生活補給品一酒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.82,0:19:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵擋惡靈侵擾的必需品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發酵過的液體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.42,0:19:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去買油 鹽 面粉和培根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以免我忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.02,0:19:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我開始恨不得自己排行老六
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒死那個女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒死那個女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.66,0:20:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 且慢 且慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果她是女巫 那就交給我處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是獵魔師葛瑞戈裡的學徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.54,0:20:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的 我看到獵魔師走進酒館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.98,0:20:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據我專業的判斷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.94,0:20:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她真的很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.54,0:20:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-要把你師父請來嗎 -不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.98,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以把她帶去處理掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.62,0:20:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我需要鹽 面粉和油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.18,0:20:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順便放幾片培根當做酬勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.06,0:21:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要怎麼處置我 學徒先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.18,0:21:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還不確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不相信我是女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看起來不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.58,0:21:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的以為自己可以成為獵魔師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你感覺太善良了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.66,0:21:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道他的學徒都死了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.86,0:21:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湯姆 你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次再告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以預知未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會再相見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.14,0:21:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跟你師父提到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.38,0:21:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不喜歡秘密嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.46,0:22:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.74,0:22:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.18,0:22:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉上眼睛就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.78,0:23:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.22,0:23:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.30,0:23:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.94,0:23:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.62,0:23:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟你母親一樣忠誠嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.98,0:23:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她就是你派去跟蹤葛瑞戈裡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.50,0:23:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡你的尖頭鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.14,0:23:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.18,0:23:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麗茲…真沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.34,0:23:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡情享用血蛋糕吧 小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.58,0:23:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才會有力氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.30,0:24:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血月之日就快來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.90,0:24:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血月能量愈強 我們魔力就會愈大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.78,0:24:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要召喚其他黑暗勢力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.94,0:24:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位兄弟姐妹 潘朵山歡迎大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.34,0:24:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的女王回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.14,0:24:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再蘑薯了 華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.30,0:24:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.06,0:24:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我說話時要叫獵魔師葛瑞戈裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.54,0:24:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獵魔師葛瑞戈裡 既然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.46,0:24:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是你的新學徒 上一個學徒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.54,0:24:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爛問題 爛問題只會得到爛答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.30,0:24:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.06,0:24:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只是游魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.82,0:25:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,級數六的魂魄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.98,0:25:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這整片森林都是游魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.59,0:25:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要惹毛他們 他們就會放你走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.50,0:25:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對獵魔師的工作了解多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.10,0:25:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獵殺惡靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.46,0:25:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的答案…讓我覺得好威啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.58,0:25:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是在控制惡靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:36.02,0:25:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些害處不大 像游魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.58,0:25:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最危險的像是女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.45,0:25:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要誘捕或殺掉她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.02,0:25:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上一個學徒都會寫筆記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.54,0:25:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是喔 但他死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.02,0:25:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是說他一定有做錯什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.38,0:26:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威廉布萊德利是我最優秀的學徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.56,0:26:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他死在瑪爾金女王手裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.88,0:26:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女巫女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.14,0:26:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以為那只是傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.38,0:26:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在所處的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.23,0:26:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說和惡夢都是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.34,0:26:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪爾金還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.82,0:26:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要去她位於潘朵山的碉堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.94,0:26:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她肯定躲在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.34,0:26:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.82,0:26:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.50,0:26:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你昏倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.06,0:26:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被施了什麼魔咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.02,0:26:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.58,0:26:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以看見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.94,0:26:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒發生的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.34,0:26:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可能有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.66,0:26:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然不是指昏倒這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.61,0:26:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是預見未來…我猜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.90,0:27:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-那是什麼 -你說他嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:07.18,0:27:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是尖牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.74,0:27:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很醜但很忠心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.34,0:27:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於你所預見的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:20.58,0:27:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有改變它們的能力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:24.66,0:27:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.42,0:27:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有真的試過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.18,0:27:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要用一點心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:32.09,0:27:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生命的詛咒通常可以變成天賦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:41.10,0:27:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的小寶貝 我就知道它們會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.42,0:27:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好照顧它們 尖牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.50,0:27:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:56.82,0:27:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甜蜜的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.50,0:28:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太不可思議了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:07.50,0:28:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去潘朵山之前 我們要准備好武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.66,0:28:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來 華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.02,0:28:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"獵鷹騎士"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:25.62,0:28:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"崇高的騎士團"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:28.18,0:28:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"致力於對抗黑暗勢力"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.10,0:28:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"有責任把知識和能力…"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:34.22,0:28:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"傳承給第七個兒子的第七個兒子"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.54,0:28:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡說你們有一千人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:42.86,0:28:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是很古老的掛畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.86,0:28:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們不是死了 就是投靠黑暗勢力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.06,0:28:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當你對付黑暗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.70,0:28:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑暗也會滲透你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:58.74,0:29:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…只剩下你一個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:09.06,0:29:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以只剩下你一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.61,0:29:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獵魔師葛瑞戈裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.76,0:29:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你提醒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:22.42,0:29:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獵魔師要接受多久的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:24.98,0:29:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我上一個學徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.38,0:29:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訓練了十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:30.22,0:29:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你 不到一個禮拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:34.50,0:29:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何這麼短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.66,0:29:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為血月就要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:39.10,0:29:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一百年發生一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:41.78,0:29:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次帶來數年的戰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.86,0:29:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女巫大肆破壞城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:48.34,0:29:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個世界至今還在重建
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:51.78,0:29:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我們不在下次血月來臨前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.70,0:29:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止瑪爾金女王…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.74,0:30:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我們何以… -夠了 別再問了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.06,0:30:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天一亮就出發 乖乖待在房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.62,0:30:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獵魔師葛瑞戈裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.93,0:30:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我學習就要解釋清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.62,0:30:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間 我們要趁瑪爾金整軍以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:10.91,0:30:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先抵達潘朵山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.70,0:30:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些女巫真該死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:15.70,0:30:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該死的女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.98,0:30:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫幫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:40.34,0:30:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫幫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.14,0:30:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.34,0:33:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我告訴過你乖乖待在房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:05.46,0:33:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是第一項考驗 華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:08.10,0:33:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一點也不驚訝 你失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:12.98,0:33:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二項考驗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.78,0:33:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花揪木魔杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:17.07,0:33:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一位獵鷹騎士制作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.98,0:33:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界上最好的戰鬥魔杖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:23.66,0:33:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕馭它…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:25.54,0:33:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能駕馭任何武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:30.50,0:33:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秀出你的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.70,0:33:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我花很多錢買你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:35.66,0:33:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸騙了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:38.42,0:33:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是第七個兒子生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.31,0:33:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七個兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:43.18,0:33:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該比一般人強壯七倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.74,0:33:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:48.90,0:33:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她也沒有留住你的意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:05.18,0:34:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一點用處也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:06.98,0:34:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間不多了 你一個禮拜內就會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:17.42,0:34:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:19.30,0:34:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我其實想瞄准你的頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.22,0:34:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:25.62,0:34:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教導我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:29.38,0:34:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:34.94,0:34:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血月升起之時 加上瑪爾金的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.38,0:34:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邪惡生物將會趁勢而起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:42.06,0:34:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變得更加強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:44.38,0:34:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些是她的左右手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:46.70,0:34:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是拉杜 他擁有刺客兵團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:56.70,0:34:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丟出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:01.70,0:35:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:08.58,0:35:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鹽和鐵…不可或缺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:12.38,0:35:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鹽可以燒傷邪惡生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:14.10,0:35:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵可以消耗他們的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.20,0:35:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銅藥酒…治療皮肉傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:19.26,0:35:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀液…驅逐女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:23.88,0:35:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,食人魔的蛋蛋…讓你自己爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:28.36,0:35:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丟石怪和開膛怪不要搞混了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:31.98,0:35:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.86,0:35:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丟石怪丟石頭 開膛怪開膛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:38.26,0:35:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名字說得很清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:53.30,0:35:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛巴南…抵擋魔咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.70,0:36:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡心 這要克什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.22,0:36:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孬種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.86,0:36:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩瑞金 化身為獵豹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:05.50,0:36:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,韋拉哈卓是劍王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.78,0:36:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我滿佩服你可以丟得一樣爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.18,0:36:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他們之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:22.22,0:36:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪爾金功力最強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.50,0:36:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:26.50,0:36:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道嗎 我預見過瑪爾金女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:31.38,0:36:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不是鹽和鐵就可以打敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:35.82,0:36:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪爾金讓我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.70,0:36:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續讀你的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:58.86,0:37:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:03.90,0:37:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這禮物…紀念你平安歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.78,0:37:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最優秀的刺客團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.86,0:37:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉杜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.10,0:37:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你寵壞我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:16.10,0:37:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你還是自己留著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.53,0:37:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會比我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:20.42,0:37:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你難道忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:22.78,0:37:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有多少自以為殺得了我的獵魔師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:25.18,0:37:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都葬身在這座山頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.54,0:37:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,血月來臨之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:29.81,0:37:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葛瑞戈裡會是下一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:44.94,0:37:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:51.38,0:37:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千萬不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:01.98,0:38:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是你最優秀的刺客團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:05.26,0:38:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以自己留著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.78,0:38:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.26,0:38:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.46,0:38:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是我姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:21.26,0:38:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她把我治好了 愛莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.50,0:38:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到血月之時 她會統治全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.14,0:38:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就能受她庇護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.22,0:38:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用再躲躲藏藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.14,0:38:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用再怕人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.14,0:38:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:39.94,0:38:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要怕她就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.14,0:38:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓她傷害你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.18,0:38:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去 給我監視獵魔師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.46,0:39:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.30,0:39:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在月光下游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:57.30,0:39:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:24.14,0:40:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:27.10,0:40:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說女巫第一次沐浴在月光下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.58,0:40:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇到她的真命天子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:35.38,0:40:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會發出藍光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.62,0:40:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你是女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:42.66,0:40:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父親是吉普賽人 我媽是女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:47.50,0:40:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我也是女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:54.98,0:40:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是我的全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:03.62,0:41:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不像你師父說的都是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.66,0:41:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有好女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:12.18,0:41:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有壞女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:15.50,0:41:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有不知道自己是女巫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:19.98,0:41:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是哪一種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.34,0:41:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:34.34,0:41:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潘朵山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:37.18,0:41:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼想變得跟他一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:41.18,0:41:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他對待你連狗都不如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.00,0:41:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還很憎恨女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:46.76,0:41:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一直在監視我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:50.66,0:41:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:53.22,0:41:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:55.02,0:41:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憎恨人類的女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:08.38,0:42:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:11.22,0:42:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:13.42,0:42:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是尖牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:15.90,0:42:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他正在做惡夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.18,0:42:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很好奇怪物做惡夢會夢到什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:24.42,0:42:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:41.54,0:42:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有乖乖把學到的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.09,0:42:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫在日志嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.90,0:42:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記憶力很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:48.90,0:42:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.26,0:42:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鬼魂和游魂有什麼不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:54.90,0:42:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鬼魂是完整的靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:56.34,0:42:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,游魂是被遺留下來的靈魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:59.26,0:43:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.18,0:43:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:07.26,0:43:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你瞄准 尖牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.58,0:43:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-什麼聲音 -鐘聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:15.74,0:43:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人召喚我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:25.54,0:43:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖牙 你最好躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.14,0:43:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是葛瑞戈裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:37.46,0:43:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要看問的人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:42.86,0:43:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們誠摯邀請你去寨城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:45.62,0:43:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗教審判官要我帶你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:50.46,0:43:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這會耗掉我們兩天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.14,0:43:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果比幻形怪還要小咖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:56.47,0:43:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就馬上離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:58.50,0:44:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼是幻形怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:00.26,0:44:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會想知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:04.62,0:44:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魔鬼就在附近 大屠殺就快發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:07.94,0:44:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邪惡的征兆無所不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.70,0:44:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我們面對的怪獸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.90,0:44:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前所未見 教士都不敢靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:17.62,0:44:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你應該更有能力保護我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:21.46,0:44:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奉承也不錯 但黃金更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:34.78,0:44:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺有點輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:36.66,0:44:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完事以後再給尾款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:48.82,0:44:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:51.50,0:44:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪爾金最嗜血的助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:54.86,0:44:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他殺過的獵魔師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:56.27,0:44:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超過其他助手的總和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:58.26,0:44:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他叫尤拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:04.02,0:45:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三個兵團才把他制伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:07.10,0:45:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是唯一的幸存者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:08.66,0:45:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們都走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:11.18,0:45:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把門鎖好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:34.34,0:45:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:37.14,0:45:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-為什麼 -古老的榮譽規則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:42.06,0:45:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更重要的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:43.38,0:45:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想跟人分酬勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:10.38,0:46:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你選錯行了 小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:59.46,0:47:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個籠子 抓好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:09.42,0:47:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:32.38,0:47:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀液
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:55.98,0:47:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒結束 油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:59.38,0:48:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:02.54,0:48:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:14.10,0:48:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:17.38,0:48:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除非你想要吃他的心髒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:40.50,0:48:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:46.74,0:48:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不像你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:49.78,0:48:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:56.94,0:48:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你會變得跟我一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:06.14,0:49:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退回去 你們都後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:10.64,0:49:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他們弄走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:30.82,0:49:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我訓練你殺女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:33.74,0:49:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做不到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:35.09,0:49:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我一點用處也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:40.18,0:49:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好 繼續賭氣啊 小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:03.82,0:50:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:24.30,0:50:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我的女王 -薩瑞金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:29.02,0:50:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,韋拉哈卓 劍王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:33.70,0:50:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史崔克斯 勇敢的巫師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:40.06,0:50:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好 大家都到了 獨缺尤拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:43.66,0:50:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:56.30,0:50:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你師父呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:02.66,0:51:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:09.38,0:51:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做不到他那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:13.06,0:51:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:15.54,0:51:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:17.38,0:51:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會使壞是一件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:21.42,0:51:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:37.26,0:51:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在古老的咒語書查了藍光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:41.58,0:51:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時候藍光和命運有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:44.26,0:51:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時候只是女巫指上的灰塵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:50.58,0:51:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以沒有特殊意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:58.74,0:52:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你師父曾經愛上女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:02.66,0:52:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時他還很年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:05.62,0:52:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們都有秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:07.66,0:52:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:12.38,0:52:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:24.74,0:52:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:57.58,0:52:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想永遠待在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:02.82,0:53:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,半調子獵魔師和半調子女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:05.90,0:53:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:09.82,0:53:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我媽教過我偷東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:13.86,0:53:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有心就會做得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:16.94,0:53:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.66,0:53:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:22.02,0:53:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我們怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:29.34,0:53:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶你離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:33.02,0:53:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去一個安全的地方 一個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:36.38,0:53:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用管這些戰爭的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:40.22,0:53:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽起來不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:47.06,0:53:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但沒有這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:09.18,0:54:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要回去找他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:18.38,0:54:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想離開你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:34.66,0:54:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可以逃避命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:06.62,0:55:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當時也是很年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:09.94,0:55:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼話都聽不進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:11.78,0:55:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你一樣傲慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:17.78,0:55:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾經愛上一個女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:21.94,0:55:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:23.46,0:55:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是瑪爾金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:30.82,0:55:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不是一直都很邪惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:33.98,0:55:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐懼和怨恨讓她變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:38.66,0:55:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為大家所想像的樣子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:41.60,0:55:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,致人於死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:44.42,0:55:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且當她…發現我已經結婚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:51.24,0:55:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她無法看著我幸福…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:57.82,0:56:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是無情地殺了我妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:06.02,0:56:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我抓到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:10.04,0:56:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很聰明 謊稱我還愛著她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:18.86,0:56:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明有機會殺了她 但我心軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:26.02,0:56:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誘騙她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:28.38,0:56:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把她關在地底的籠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:34.10,0:56:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以為可以永遠關住她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:38.54,0:56:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:42.22,0:56:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她逃走後殺的人 都是我害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:51.54,0:56:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想跟你介紹我妻子 華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:56.38,0:56:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是蕾貝佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:00.58,0:57:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的死…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:02.78,0:57:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我對你如此嚴厲的原因 湯姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:14.86,0:57:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:19.26,0:57:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到女巫…就把她殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:25.30,0:57:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我女兒發現他們愈來愈接近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:30.58,0:57:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個男孩任憑你處理 親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:35.26,0:57:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但葛瑞戈裡留給我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:38.10,0:57:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要活口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:49.06,0:57:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越過那座森林就是潘朵山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:51.62,0:57:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們還有三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:56.54,0:57:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:58.30,0:58:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:21.22,0:58:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:22.50,0:58:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻形怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:24.14,0:58:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地底怪獸 脾氣很差 跟蝙蝠一樣瞎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:28.30,0:58:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼打幻形怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:29.82,0:58:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不打幻形怪 只管逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:56.02,0:58:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尖牙 快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:59.06,0:59:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:14.22,0:59:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是說幻形怪很瞎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:16.10,0:59:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但嗅覺…很靈敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:20.26,0:59:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:43.38,0:59:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們似乎遇到幻形怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:47.90,0:59:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:55.26,0:59:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別慌…我們現在安全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:59.06,1:00:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻形怪…很討厭水
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:19.34,1:00:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:21.66,1:00:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.06,1:00:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:25.13,1:00:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碰到幻形怪 你就變得很不可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.62,1:00:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湯姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:01.22,1:01:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湯姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.74,1:02:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再想著愛莉絲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:18.26,1:02:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你師父想要獵殺我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:20.35,1:02:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒死我們 吃我們的心髒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:23.26,1:02:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把你的心髒挖出來給你吃如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:32.06,1:02:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那塊寶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:34.42,1:02:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我女王的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:36.42,1:02:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會在你手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:04.10,1:03:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:05.90,1:03:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用起來 我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:08.62,1:03:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很好 只是殺了一頭恐怖的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:12.22,1:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:13.78,1:03:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會這麼容易死的吧 華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:19.54,1:03:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還殺了殺不死的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:52.82,1:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從哪裡弄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:55.02,1:03:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我媽給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:00.34,1:04:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:02.50,1:04:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:06.14,1:04:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑你啊 華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:12.18,1:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:13.46,1:04:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 暗黑晶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:17.58,1:04:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女巫最神聖的護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:20.10,1:04:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以讓她們變得更強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:22.46,1:04:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓她們的幻覺變得更真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:26.54,1:04:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會在我媽手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:32.94,1:04:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪爾金女王…曾經擁有這塊寶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:37.26,1:04:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那寶石在她手上 產生無窮的魔力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:42.18,1:04:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但後來被別的女巫偷走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:47.10,1:04:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才有機會制伏她
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:49.86,1:04:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誘捕她
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:54.28,1:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說我媽是女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:01.62,1:05:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你也是女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:05.38,1:05:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女巫的兒子竟然是獵魔師的學徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:10.66,1:05:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:18.10,1:05:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的預視能力就說得通了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:30.98,1:05:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:34.00,1:05:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有活要干
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:42.26,1:05:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤拉怎麼了
