Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:49.62,1:05:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遺憾讓你看到這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:53.42,1:05:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個獵魔師很冷血
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:56.30,1:05:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他逮到機會也會這樣對你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:59.50,1:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個學徒也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:03.46,1:06:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湯姆是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:06.22,1:06:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惜他快死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:08.30,1:06:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不希望他死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:11.94,1:06:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以救他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:14.82,1:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湯姆愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:17.62,1:06:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你媽媽發現他真心愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:20.50,1:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就連暗黑晶石也隱藏不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:27.66,1:06:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你媽在湯姆的脖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:30.34,1:06:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現那塊寶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:35.98,1:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿回我被偷走的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:39.14,1:06:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的男孩就免於一死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:41.18,1:06:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼知道你說的是真是假
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:45.18,1:06:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我拿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:57.50,1:07:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓那些燒死女巫的城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:00.70,1:07:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道我們的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:03.02,1:07:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要為兄弟尤拉報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:05.58,1:07:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓人類嘗嘗毀滅的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:52.78,1:07:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:54.38,1:07:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:11.28,1:08:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地獄降臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:53.10,1:08:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫幫我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:46.06,1:09:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我要回去 -不
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:47.70,1:09:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要讓她受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:54.30,1:09:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:14.18,1:10:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一個女巫在保護這座城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:26.10,1:10:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女巫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:32.06,1:10:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背信忘義的小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:36.94,1:10:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們被殲滅的時候 你背棄我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:41.26,1:10:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:44.42,1:10:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們知道你的身分…就會憎恨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:52.78,1:10:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本可以救你的東西 卻給了別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:58.18,1:11:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那份大禮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:00.78,1:11:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會害死你兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.46,1:11:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你淪為黑暗勢力的奴隸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:06.43,1:11:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪爾金女王 你根本稱不上女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:38.10,1:11:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可以止痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:40.50,1:11:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:42.14,1:11:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你更有人味
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:46.30,1:11:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們丟了所有行囊 你怎麼還有酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:49.46,1:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是好運吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:01.26,1:12:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一天不可以喝超過一口
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:04.62,1:12:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:05.74,1:12:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:16.54,1:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很醜但很能撐 老朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.02,1:12:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:21.34,1:12:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:27.66,1:12:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:29.22,1:12:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在這裡 我們去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:59.66,1:13:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:00.86,1:13:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要留在這裡 他們快回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:04.06,1:13:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我改變心意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:07.70,1:13:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:14.22,1:13:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你愛我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:20.30,1:13:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:31.04,1:13:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:32.42,1:13:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把木材拿來 我們要生火
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:35.86,1:13:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湯姆 不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:37.28,1:13:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說把木材拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:39.70,1:13:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退回去 師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:42.74,1:13:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-別逼我 -她是間諜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:45.74,1:13:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:47.18,1:13:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有任務在身 華德先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:49.38,1:13:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在你正面臨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:53.74,1:13:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:55.26,1:13:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別傷害他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:58.62,1:13:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:03.30,1:14:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 那塊寶石
