Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.02,1:14:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還說她是無辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:15.92,1:14:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:53.64,1:14:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不可以讓這個學徒也死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:17.70,1:15:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湯姆
