Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:56.74,1:16:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:59.26,1:17:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:01.06,1:17:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣的 湯姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:04.98,1:17:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經離開人世
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:09.36,1:17:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對抗瑪爾金女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:13.06,1:17:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:16.46,1:17:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你不會失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:19.90,1:17:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不只是第七個兒子 湯姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:22.34,1:17:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是女巫的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:25.42,1:17:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人像你一樣強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:28.26,1:17:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有你能利用暗黑晶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:31.58,1:17:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁瑪爾金還沒成功前
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:33.80,1:17:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終結黑暗國度
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:39.10,1:17:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕走心裡的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:43.62,1:17:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用勇氣填滿它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:48.26,1:17:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經准備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:51.54,1:17:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:54.78,1:17:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到那顆寶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:58.78,1:18:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:24.86,1:18:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會那麼容易死的吧
