Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:14.14,1:19:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:15.82,1:19:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要他們跟蹤你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:21.70,1:19:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以前不會這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:25.02,1:19:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是為你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:26.98,1:19:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著你的女王 就會找到平靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:41.54,1:19:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葛瑞戈裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:43.82,1:19:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:45.82,1:19:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他將再也無法帶來恐懼
