Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:57.10,1:20:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永遠…都不分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:01.42,1:20:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:03.90,1:20:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:10.26,1:20:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:20.52,1:20:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邪惡就在你心底
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:29.62,1:20:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加入我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:35.10,1:20:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可敬的敵人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:38.26,1:20:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在受到我們的尊敬…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:40.78,1:20:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:43.78,1:20:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭已經結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:46.50,1:20:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們終於在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:00.14,1:21:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:11.22,1:21:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:12.34,1:21:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別殺她 求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:18.70,1:21:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:17.82,1:22:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的項鏈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:21.06,1:22:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我弄丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:24.46,1:22:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拿走是為了保護你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:06.94,1:23:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以龍形跟我對打 而不是人形
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:11.14,1:23:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還有榮譽心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:58.66,1:24:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本不了解龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:05.98,1:24:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更不了解榮譽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:29.70,1:25:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是不要變成人形得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:06.16,1:26:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我的女王 -你干了什麼好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:08.26,1:26:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是我的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:11.34,1:26:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以為人類才會背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:55.66,1:26:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己來
