Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:36.02,1:27:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:40.06,1:27:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不恨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:19.50,1:28:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:21.70,1:28:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會…纏著…你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:41.70,1:29:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久以前…
